                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 14.) I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">read—James Smith, convicted July</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">of stealing twelve tame pigeons, confined three months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
